{"word":"ἀριφραδής","slug":"ἀριφραδής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀριφραδής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>φράζομαι</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>easy to be known, very distinct, manifest</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-δέως</el>, <i>plainly</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>very thoughtful, wise</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}